      • doesAccept

        public boolean doesAccept(java.lang.Object objectToAccept)
        A sequence diagram can accept all classifiers. It will add them as a new Classifier Role with that classifier as a base. All other accepted figs are added as is.
        Parameters:
        objectToAccept -
        Returns:
        true if the diagram can accept the object, else false
        See Also:
